Class PowerUp

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.csupomona.cs.cs141.thehouse.PowerUp
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExtraAmmo, Radar, Shield

    public abstract class PowerUp
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Kurt This is the abstract class for the powerups in the game, which are Invincibility, Radar, and an Extra Bullet. This class will have the behaviors for all the powerups and how they will interact with the character.
